Income Tax Expense
The effective income tax rate for 2022 was 21.5% compared to 17.1% in 2021. The increase in the effective rate was primarily due
to a decrease in tax benefits related to employee share-based payments and a net unfavorable impact of various other tax benefits
received by the Company in 2022 as compared to 2021. See Note 21 to the Consolidated Financial Statements in Item 8 for
